 "overview": "\u003Cp\u003EHalogen Software\u0026#8217;s web-based solutions automate and simplfy employee performance appraisal\u0026#8217;s, compensation management, succession planning and 360 degree feedback.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003ESome companies like to distinguish themselves by their size, their long list of prestigious customers, product awards and so on\u0026#8230;\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EAs a market leader, Halogen can make similar claims, but what really defines us is fairly simple \u2014 we deliver outstanding value and delight our customers. In fact we\u0026#8217;re extremely customer focused.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EOur mission is to make it easy for our customers to build a world-class workforce that is aligned, inspired and delivering exceptional results.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EWe do that with powerful, simple to use and affordable cloud-based talent management solutions. Our customers want powerful, simple and affordable.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EIt\u0026#8217;s why our entire suite was organically-built from the ground up \u2014 not bolted together. And why we\u2019re the first and only talent management vendor to offer a complete talent management suite that\u0026#8217;s purpose-built to drive performance.\u003C/p\u003E",
